doctype html
html
  head
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='css/master.scss.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='css/museum.scss.css')
    title Museum of the Future
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='robots', content='INDEX, FOLLOW')
    meta(name='viewport',content='width=device-width, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no')
  body
    .wrapper.header-wrapper
      header.clear-fix
        div
          a(href="")
            img(src="static/logo.svg" alt="Museum of the Future")
        ul
          li
            a(href="#demo", data-scroll-to="demo") Try it Now
          li
            a(href="#tech", data-scroll-to="tech") Tech
          li
            a(href="#contact", data-scroll-to="contact") Talk to Us
    main(ng-controller="mainController")
      .wrapper.section-wrapper.feature.bg-blue
        section.clear-fix
          div
            h1 Museum of the Future
            p.
              A museum about everything you care about and love &mdash; a unique insight into your own world, built just for you.
            button(id="make-a-museum").bg-blue
              span Make my Museum
              span.right.fa.fa-caret-right
      .wrapper.section-wrapper.bg-white#demo
        section.clear-fix
          div#demo-container
            .museum.clear-fix#colours
              .room-width
              .room#room-red
                .walls
                  .wall.left.pieces
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0)")
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(204, 0, 0)")
                  .wall.right.pieces
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(153, 0, 0)")
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(102, 0, 0)")
                  .wall.top
                  .wall.bottom
                  .wall.back.piece
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(51, 0, 0)")
                .overlay
                //- .overlay
                //-   div.bottom
                //-     p
                //-       |&copy; Museum of the Future, 2014 &mdash;
              .room#room-green
                .walls
                  .wall.left.pieces
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 255, 0)")
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 204, 0)")
                  .wall.right.pieces
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 153, 0)")
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 102, 0)")
                  .wall.top
                  .wall.bottom
                  .wall.back.piece
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 51, 0)")
                .overlay
              .room#room-blue
                .walls
                  .wall.left.pieces
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255)")
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 204)")
                  .wall.right.pieces
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 153)")
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 102)")
                  .wall.top
                  .wall.bottom
                  .wall.back.piece
                    .piece.hang-high
                      .blank(style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 51)")
                .overlay
              .side
                .side-inner
                  button(id="show-red-room-button").gray Show Red Room
                  button(id="show-green-room-button").gray Show Green Room
                  button(id="show-blue-room-button").gray Show Blue Room
                  p.
                    Hello, World.
      .wrapper.section-wrapper.bg-green
        section.clear-fix
          div.icon-left
            h1 What is it?
            p.
              We love museums. We think it's really important that the knowledge of humanity is preserved and accessible forever! But museums have to be exciting and interesting as well.
            p.
              Imagine a museum about everything you actually care about and love (and more) &mdash; a unique insight into your own world, built just for you.
            p.
              Welcome to a museum where the exhibits belong to you. Welcome to Museum of the Future.
          div.icon-right
            span.fa.fa-star-o
      .wrapper.section-wrapper.bg-purple
        section.clear-fix
          div.icon-left
            h1 It&rsquo;s all about You
            p.
              Museums are full of fascinating things, but in a world where whatever you want to know is just a click away, something has to change to make the museum relevant and as eye-opening as it used to be.
            p.
              Museum of the Future works out your interests from your Twitter or Facebook posts (or you can choose what tickles your fancy yourself). They're then brought to life in a vibrant 3D experience with exhibits from all over the Web.
          div.icon-right
            span.fa.fa-thumbs-o-up
      .wrapper.section-wrapper.hide.bg-red.tall#tech
        section.clear-fix
          div.icon-left
            h1 The Fizz, Bangs and Whistles
            p.
              Hello, World.
          div.icon-right
            span.fa.fa-terminal
      .wrapper.section-wrapper.hide.bg-yellow.tall#contact
        section.clear-fix
          div.icon-left
            h1 Let's Work Together
            p.
              Hello, World.
          div.icon-right
            span.fa.fa-envelope-o
    .wrapper.footer-wrapper
      footer.clear-fix
        div.logo
          p
            span.fa.fa-university
        div
          ul
            li
              a(href="#demo", data-scroll-to="demo") Try it Now
            li
              a(href="#tech", data-scroll-to="tech") Tech
            li
              a(href="#contact", data-scroll-to="contact") Talk to Us
        //- div
        //-   ul
        //-     li
        //-       a(href="") Our Clients
        //-     li
        //-       a(href="") Press
    script(src='js/jquery.min.js')
    script(src='js/async.js')
    script(src='js/museum.js')
    script(src='js/master.js')